		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Pretty cool.  I was planning on making a controller for my 7800 sometime, but I hadn't considered modding the reset and select buttons like that, I might have to steal that idea.  7800 games don't rely on those as much, but I do play enough 2600 games on it.

		

