		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yes. The 7800 Buttons work a funky way or I might have made it compatible. I'm sure it will work fine for 2600 games though. On a side note the external power and ground are completely unnecessary. I added them on the off chance there is a special Neo Geo joystick that needs more power.

		

